        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_092_000104",
    "sentence": "承範溫厚寡言，善希人旨，桑維翰、李崧尤重之，嘗薦於高祖，雲可大用。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "桑維翰",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_092_000105",
    "sentence": "承範知之，持重自養，雖遇盛夏，而猶服襦袴，加之以純綿，蓋慮有寒濕之患也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_092_000106",
    "sentence": "然竟不獲其志，其命也夫！",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_092_000107",
    "sentence": "盧導，字熙化，其先范陽人也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_092_000108",
    "sentence": "祖伯卿，唐殿中侍御史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 8,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_092_000109",
    "sentence": "父如晦，國子監丞，贈戶部侍郎。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "侍郎",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_092_000110",
    "sentence": "導少而儒雅，美詞翰，善談論。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
